ent_type=3D"widget" data-e-type=3D"widget" data-widget_type=3D"text-editor.=
default"><p>With over 28 years in the entertainment industry, Eva Scolaro i=
sn=E2=80=99t just a performer=E2=80=94she=E2=80=99s a force of nature. Fuel=
ed by passion and an unstoppable creative spirit, Eva brings unforgettable =
energy to every stage she steps on. From the age of 5, Eva has been captiva=
ting audiences, lighting up stages across Indonesia and Southeast Asia with=
 her undeniable talent. Her versatility is unmatched=E2=80=94whether she=E2=
=80=99s delivering smooth, soulful jazz, crooning timeless classics, or unl=
eashing her powerhouse vocal house sound (recognized by Tiesto), Eva Scolar=
o is pure fire.&nbsp;</p></div><div class=3D"elementor-element elementor-el=
ement-a34a308 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id=3D"a34=
a308" data-element_type=3D"widget" data-e-type=3D"widget" data-widget_type=
=3D"text-editor.default"><div>She=E2=80=99s not just a performer, she=E2=80=
=99s an experience that touches your soul. Fresh off recording her first so=
lo album in Spain, Eva has just released her latest single, =E2=80=9CDeeper=
 Love=E2=80=9D. You can now dive into her latest work on Spotify and iTunes=
.</div><p><a href=3D"https://open.spotify.com/artist/1Cnhz3VFCwxhAgrvrCOXlT=
?si=3DYW5CRx18SCCOkJ-TphkHPg" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noopener">LISTEN NOW=
!</a></p></div><div class=3D"elementor-element elementor-element-9cffd5d el=
ementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id=3D"9cffd5d" data-eleme=
nt_type=3D"widget" data-e-type=3D"widget" data-widget_type=3D"text-editor.d=
efault"><p>Eva has made her dream full circle. Bringing the knowledge and e=
xperience of performing arts that she had as a child, which has proven true=
 and brought her so much success in her career to date. To now share this w=
ith the younger generations so they may experience the joy of the stage.</p=
